101112.name: Summer Starts Now II
101112.description: It's clearly a holiday, but you see folks at work everywhere.

101113.name: Summer Starts Now III
101113.description: A coconut tree that bears eggs? Then we should call it...

102080.name: Getting up There
102080.description: There's a path here, so let's just use this quietly to get up there without disturbing it.

102111.name: Mystery Easter Egg I
102111.description: Help! Is there anyone out there?!
params_des: Defeat duckies with the hammer to get points.

102112.name: Mystery Easter Egg II
102112.description: Captain Sekhmet, the Administrator of Aether Gazer is looking for you. Please respond as soon as you hear this broadcast.

102113.name: Mystery Easter Egg III
102113.description: Just what do cats make of the beach when they see one...? I mean, there's both sand and water here.

201080.name: On That Side of the Sea
201080.description: There's a path here, so let's just use this quietly to get over to the other side without disturbing it.

201082.name: On That Side of the Sea
201082.description: There's a path here, so let's just use this quietly to get over to the other side without disturbing it.

201111.name: Great Nautical Race I
201111.description: Suddenly... something pokes out of the bushes: a crocodile head!
params_des: Tap on the bubbles and eliminate all bubbles to get points.

201112.name: Great Nautical Race II
201112.description: What? The head coach is warming up right now?!
params_des: Drive the speedboat and reach the endpoint within the time given.

201113.name: Great Nautical Race III
201113.description: The real competition continues even after the race!

202111.name: Fugitive Sun I
202111.description: When the woods start to go quack, quack...
params_des: Defeat duckies with the hammer to get points.

202112.name: Fugitive Sun II
202112.description: Sometimes, it's not a good thing to be too popular.
params_des: Play notes according to the beat to defeat the enemy.

203111.name: The Ducky & AGI Mecha Crisis I
203111.description: Our highly advanced ducky has totally surpassed those outdated AGI Mechas!

203112.name: The Ducky & AGI Mecha Crisis II
203112.description: Stop it! Stop fighting now, all of you!!!
params_des: Play notes according to the beat to defeat the enemy.

301070.name: Park CS Counter
301070.description: You know, the business paid to advertise, so we can't exactly ask them to move to another spot without a really good reason.

301073.name: Park CS Counter
301073.description: You know, the business paid to advertise, so we can't exactly ask them to move to another spot without a really good reason.

301111.name: The Sound of Music I
301111.description: Once you eliminate all the wrong answers, only the correct one will be left!

301112.name: The Sound of Music II
301112.description: Listen to the tune below and choose the correct answer. E.g.: The price of the shirt is...?

301113.name: The Sound of Music III
301113.description: You ask what's so great about Ducky? Well, Ducky is... Um... what's so great about Ducky again?
params_des: Play notes according to the beat to defeat the enemy.

302111.name: Fugitive Duck I
302111.description:
AHHHH! Those wild thieving ducks have made their way out!
Charge, my knights!!!

302112.name: Fugitive Duck II
302112.description: You can stop right here, ducky. You're surrounded, there are knights everywhere outside.
params_des: Play notes according to the beat to defeat the enemy.

303111.name: The Great Thievers I
303111.description: Come on, Zero One! Give everyone a reason to gasp!
params_des: Tap on the bubbles and eliminate all bubbles to get points.

303112.name: The Great Thievers I
303112.description: Surrender is out of the question. Not today, not in this lifetime.
params_des: Play notes according to the beat to defeat the enemy.

401111.name: Water Cannon Battle I
401111.description:
Why aren't you eliminated yet???
Meat shields, kiddo.

401112.name: Water Cannon Battle II
401112.description:
You've got your weapon, now come with me.
It's time to grab us some treasures.
params_des: Piece together the puzzle pieces to produce the puzzle image.

401113.name: Water Cannon Battle III
401113.description: First, do not deliberate and do the absolute first thing that comes to mind; second, the refs won't see the bad parts; and third, the refereeing won't be fair at all. Captain of the AGI Mecha Referees requests a meeting with you!
params_des: Use the water weapon to fire at the enemy and break out.

401114.name: Water Cannon Battle IV
401114.description:
Battling is the only way to survive!
To win, use the steel fist against the duckies!
params_des: Use SkyNova to destroy the giant duck.

402111.name: Mecha Rumble I
402111.description: Yell out the moves to battle the AGI Mechas? It may sound a little childish to the kids, but it works just fine for us.

402112.name: Mecha Rumble II
402112.description: Seriously, one should know when to stop fooling around.
params_des: Catch the troublemaking duckies and take them to the designated area within the time given.

403111.name: Moment of Peace and Love I
403111.description:
This image is titled "Admin and Senba on Vacation." But where are Admin and Senba?
Admin and Senba are standing in line.

403112.name: Moment of Peace and Love II
403112.description: It's over now! You stood in line for two hours just to surf for five minutes!

501111.name: Just One More Step I
501111.description: My friends, I've missed you so much!!!

501112.name: Just One More Step II
501112.description: No matter if it's a big hammer or a small hammer, now it's hammer time!
params_des: Piece together the puzzle pieces to produce the puzzle image.

501114.name: Just One More Step IV
501114.description: Enough chatter about friendship, bonds, the future, and all that. Just charge!!!
params_des: Use SkyNova to destroy the Mecha Centaur.

502111.name: Mystery Gift I
params_des: Catch the troublemaking duckies and take them to the designated area within the time given.

502112.name: Mystery Gift II
502112.description: All the dazzling moments you've ever had in your life will become precious, shining memories that last forever.
